in which we have been engaged, will be eminently useful. And it adds not a little to the firmness of my conviction of the propriety the proceeding I have taken the liberty to recommend, to find, that I the most laborious research at last brings us back to the same conclusion, to which daily observation, and plain common sense, at once conducted the body of the nation;

